scenes.description: Title card for the 3D Birthday event: Secret Agent Test.
Vestia Zeta sneaks onto the stage as part of her secret agent role-play.
Vestia Zeta addresses the audience, celebrates her birthday, and introduces the 'Secret Agent Test' challenge.
Transition to a wasteland scene where Sakura Miko and AZKi encounter a monster.
